# Middle mouse (wheel click) → desktopUI: single primary display only.
#
# 1. Copy to your Hyprland config dir or merge into hyprland.conf:
#      source = /ABS/PATH/TO/desktopUI/hypr/desktopui-primary-mouse.conf
# 2. Fix the path below (must be absolute, no spaces before commas).
# 3. If nothing happens, run `wev` and press the wheel; try mouse:273 instead of 274.

# bind = , mouse:274, exec, /home/USER/Programs/desktopUI/bin/desktopui-primary-display
